{{flavour|Manifests the caster's faith as a spiritual weapon, which will fight and slay the caster's enemies under its own power.

As it is a direct reflection of the caster's unique zeal, the weapon they receive from their god will be the same each time.}}

The spell summons a single [[dancing weapon]], either an [[axe]] or [[polearm]]. Depending on the [[spell power]], it can be a [[war axe]]/[[trident]], [[battleaxe]]/[[glaive]] of [[electrocution]], or [[executioner's axe]]/[[bardiche]] of [[speed (brand)|speed]].

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|this [[Beogh]] apostle-only spell will be added to the game.}}

